00094 // Compute -Cf.psi.U.|U|/sqrt(K).dvol
00095 inline void Eval_Forchheimer_VEF_Face::calculer_terme_source(int num_face, DoubleVect& source, const DoubleVect& volumes) const
00096 {
00097   int size=source.size();
00098   for (int i=0; i<size; i++)
00099     {
00100       double U = vitesse->valeurs()(num_face,i);
00101       source(i) = -Cf/sqrt(modK->getK(porosite))*volumes(num_face)*porosite_surf(num_face)*dabs(U)*U;
00102     }
00103 }
00104 
00105 inline void Eval_Forchheimer_VEF_Face::calculer_terme_source_standard(int num_face, DoubleVect& source) const
00106 {
00107   calculer_terme_source(num_face, source, volumes_entrelaces);
00108 }
